1. Error middleware + 404 handler (prevents crashes / stack-trace leaks).
2. `helmet`, rate limiting, body size cap, disable `x-powered-by`.
3. AuthN/AuthZ on `/users` and remove unnecessary PII.
4. Schema-based input validation as new routes are added.
5. Structured logging + graceful shutdown.

